short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays a list of all opened tabs in the browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Opened Tabs is a browser extension for Google Chrome that helps users manage and navigate their opened tabs. With Opened Tabs, users can view a listing of all opened tabs in the browser and quickly switch between them by clicking on links.

One of the key features of Opened Tabs is its intuitive and user-friendly interface. When users click on the extension's button in the browser toolbar, a pop-up window appears displaying a list of all opened tabs. Each tab is represented by a link that displays the tab's title. Users can easily scan the list of tabs and click on a link to navigate to the corresponding tab.
